     *                           Ignored if there's no valid pending intent.
     * @param handler handler to be used to call onFinishedListener
     *                Ignored if there's no valid pending intent.
     * @see PendingIntent#send(Context, int, Intent, PendingIntent.OnFinished, Handler)
     